From 50319163cfd48659d48d645bad1b2d3b56000e91 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Pete via Claude <mrpeteroesler@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Apr 2026 18:20:53 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] feat(payload): add Pueblos, Pages, Guides collections

Adds three new Payload collections (Pueblos, Pages, Guides) per spec
with localized fields, public read / admin write access, and SEO
groups. Also adds a Media collection to back upload relations, wires
payload localization (es default, en fallback), and exposes a
generate:types npm script.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
